) – All legs heterotridactylous, medial claw thicker and larger than lateral claws. Formulae of leg setation and solenidia: I (1-5-3-4-19) [1-2-2], II (1-5-2-4-15) [1-1-2], III (2- 3-1-3-15) [1-1-0], IV (1-2-2-3-12) [0-1-0] (
Table 1
